title: You Are Not It
description:
You’re more than what you’re going through. In “You Are Not It,” Pastor Steven Furtick of Elevation Church reveals that God doesn’t see us through the lens of what we’ve done, but for who we are.

If you’ve just made a decision for Christ, please respond here: http://ele.vc/7vUtpo
